# Design System

## Colors
- Base: Zinc gray
- Primary: TRAC Blue (#0c0563)
- Use CSS variables, never hardcode

## Typography
- Font: Rajdhani
- Section title: `text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground`
- Field label: `text-xs text-muted-foreground`
- Field value: `font-medium`

## Border Radius
- Elements: `rounded-md` or `rounded-lg`
- Badges: `rounded-full`

## Shadows
- Minimal - prefer border definition
